New & Cool Updates:
· Never again miss an update from a friend. When a friend updates their status, creates a new Movie, gives you an autograph and more, you will see an icon on your friend’s avatar.

· Bug fixes
Thanks for your feedback. We have more updates planned, so don’t forget to check in regularly.

We have some great updates for you!

-When sending an emoji to a friend on MovieStarPlanet, it will be super-sized.
-You can turn off in-game notifications when chatting to another MovieStar.
-Profile activities now include photos, how cool is that?

We have also fixed various bugs! Thank you and keep sending us feedback!

Ready for more?
- Beauty Clinic Update – When you buy a new make-up, it will now be added to your Beauty Clinic inventory, which can be accessed by clicking the new tab in your Dressing Room.
- Movie Studio Scenes – You can now make Movies by creating scenes. Create real Hollywood magic with light, camera & action!
- Commenting on Movies – Did you like a Movie? You can now comment on other MovieStars Movies.
Thanks for your feedback – You are amazing! Keep it coming!
